2. Atualizar Model Credential:
   ```php
   public function creator() {
       return $this->belongsTo(User::class, 'created_by');
   }
   public function updater() {
       return $this->belongsTo(User::class, 'updated_by');
   }
   ```
3. Atualizar CredentialController:
