1. Instalar dependências:
   ```bash
   composer require barryvdh/laravel-dompdf
   composer require maatwebsite/excel
   ```
2. Criar ReportController:
   ```php
   public function credentials(Request $request) {
       $query = Credential::query();

       if ($request->date_from) {
           $query->where('concession', '>=', $request->date_from);
       }
       if ($request->date_to) {
           $query->where('concession', '<=', $request->date_to);
       }
       if ($request->secrecy) {
           $query->where('secrecy', $request->secrecy);
       }

       $credentials = $query->with(['creator'])->get();

       if ($request->format === 'pdf') {
           $pdf = PDF::loadView('reports.credentials-pdf', compact('credentials'));
           return $pdf->download('relatorio-credenciais.pdf');
       }

       return Excel::download(new CredentialsExport($credentials), 'credenciais.xlsx');
   }
   ```
3. Criar views:
   - reports/form.blade.php (filtros de relatório)
   - reports/credentials-pdf.blade.php (template PDF)
4. Criar CredentialsExport class implementando FromCollection
5. Adicionar rotas e menu de relatórios

